The paper proposes a novel embedding method for knowledge base completion task using convolutional neural network (CNN). Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves natural language processing (NLP) techniques, which suggests the sub-category cs.CL (Computation and Language) as another likely option. Additionally, the paper deals with databases and knowledge representation, which could fall under cs.DB (Databases). Finally, the paper involves information retrieval (IR) techniques, which suggests the sub-category cs.IR as another possible option.
